\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個出發都浪漫化戰爭（同二戰好唔同）"},{"pid":"ab9a41bce836e8ef1ca5843725622f26bc3a2ada","tid":1177343,"uid":4260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T23:16:37.000Z","msg":"今日應該上最後一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}